import React from 'react'
import '../index.css'


const Login = () => {
  return (
   <>
   <form action="/login" method="post" id='form'>
      <label htmlFor="FirstName"></label>
      <input type="text" name="FirstName" id="firstname" />
      <label htmlFor="lastname"></label>
      <input type="text" name="lastname" id="name" />
      <label htmlFor="email"></label>
      <input type="email" name="email" id="email_input" />
      <label htmlFor="set-password"></label>
      <input type="password" name="set-password" id="password" />
      <label htmlFor="confirm-pass"></label>
      <input type="password" name="confirm-pass" id="confirm-password" />
      <button type="submit">Submit</button>
      </form>
   </>
  )
}

export default Login
